'''Comedy music''' is [[music]] that is [[Comedy|comic]] or [[humor]]ous in nature, encompassing a wide variety of [[music genre]]s. Popular types of comedy music include [[parody music]], [[novelty song]]s, [[comedy rock]] and [[comedy hip hop]]. Some comedians, such as [[Bo Burnham]] and [[Tim Hawkins]], use songs in stand-up in addition to more traditional joke-telling methods, while others, such as [["Weird Al" Yankovic]] and [[Lil Dicky]], focus entirely on comedy music as their sole medium of humor.

